		{"id":"f82cbaf6bcbd8408","type":"text","text":"success!\nneed better panel gutter management (precision) for claude\n\nthis baked in the style and i chose my fav visuals. i probably want to choose style back at the 12 gens\n\nclaude needs better pixel perfect panel layout and spacing tools for this workflow","x":5160,"y":1646,"width":250,"height":240},
